                Velagenus <lb n="2"/>Manti <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Ulattius <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>Alp</abbr><ex>inorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXVIII <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XVI <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Longinus |(centurio) et <lb n="9"/>Primus <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ustos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ar</abbr><ex>morum</ex></expan> b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>heredes <lb n="11"/>posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld von einer aedicula gerahmt; im Giebelfeld eine Rosette, in den Zwickeln über dem Giebel Delphine. (B): AE 1913: Z. 8: hedera anstelle des umgekehrten C für centurio; Z. 9 (Ende): b(eneficiarius).</p>
